Package: alta
Title: Active Learning for Text Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Blake", "Miller", email = "b.a.miller@lse.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4707-0984")) 
Description: ALTA provides a simple interface for document annotation using active learning. While implementing several active learning algorithms for text annotation, this package also facilitates random sampling approaches to document annotation.
